      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a small dent on the rear bumper. The interior shows significant wear on the driver's seat and some staining on the carpets. It is mechanically functional but shows signs of regular use.",
      "price": 20000.0,
